//**********************************************************************
*
*                   SETUP
*
***********************************************************************//

Install pip
  https://pip.pypa.io/en/stable/

Install and set up virtualenv
  https://virtualenv.pypa.io/en/stable/

Clone the project
    git clone https://github.com/schmidtvl/hackbot.git

  1. Name your bot or work on an existing bot
          mkdir [BOT_NAME]
          cd [BOT_NAME]
        or
          cd [EXISTING_BOT_NAME]

  2. Set up the virtualenv in env/ under root directory of your bot
          mkdir env
          virtualenv env

  3. Activate the virtual env
          source bin/env/activate

  4. Install requirements
      4a. You've created a brand new bot
            cp ../requirements.txt .
            pip install -r requirements.txt
      4b. This is an existing bot
            pip install -r requirements.txt


Now you should be set up and ready to go. Individual bots may have more specific requirements
